Joy Taylor is a seasoned national media figure who graduated from Barry University and has experience in play-by-play, events, radio, television, podcasts, moderating, and hosting. Joy moved to the opposite side of the FS1 studio after almost two years of anchoring UNDISPUTED to work with Colin Cowherd as co-host of The Herd, which airs every week from 12 to 3 PM ET.
